                            Let <me>A =
\left[\begin{array}{rr}
0 \amp 4 \\
-1 \amp 4 \\
\end{array}\right]</me>.
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                    <solution>
                        <p>
                            See <url href="https://understandinglinearalgebra.org/sec-eigen-diag.html#sec-eigen-diag-3-10">Example 4.3.6</url>.
                        </p>
                    </solution>
                    
                </exercise>
            </page>

